title: Ep. 186 -  Jetha Looks After The Kid - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Daya has gone shopping with the other ladies and Jetha has to look after the kid. Jetha does not like it as he is getting irritated with the kids who are naughty and jumpy.

title: Ep. 187 -  Awkward Situation Between Jetha And Babita - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Babita comes to visit the kid in Jetha's house. But the kid starts saying mean things about both of them which makes Jetha and Babita awkward. Watch how Jetha tries to calm Babita.

title: Ep. 188 - Dr. Hathi Arrives In A Heroic Way - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Dr. Hathi is back to the Gokuldham society after a break. He makes a heroic entry in a rented car, eating bananas. Everyone is happy to meet him after a long time.

title: Ep. 189 - Jethalal Seeks For Babita's Attention - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jethalal is praying from his balcony when he suddenly sees Babita. He starts trying hard and makes noises to gather her attention. Jethalal wants to know Babita's problem and wants to help her.

title: Ep. 190 - Jethalal Misinterpreted The Situation - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jethalal gets to know from somewhere that it is Babita's birthday. So he gets flowers for her and visits her house to give her birthday wishes. Babita tries to convey to him that it is not her birthday.

title: Ep. 191 -Jethalal Gets Panicky - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jethalal receives a call from Mehta getting to know that It's Babita's birthday and there's a party which is of a western theme. Jethalal listening to it gets worried and decides to learn western dance and while practicing gets caught by his wife.

title: Ep. 192 - Struggle Of Jethalal - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Daya reacts unexpectedly after catching Jethalal dancing with a stranger, he explains that she is a dance instructor. Later on, they find out everybody received an invitation card except them.

title: Ep. 193 - One Problem At A Time - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: A sorrowful Jethalal, after realizing the embarrassment of his family for not being invited, decides to go away. Suddenly, Babita shows up at his house and find out about the issue. She clarifies everything and finally invites them.

title: Ep. 194 - Finally Party Time - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: As it's a western-themed party, Daya tells Jethalal that she won't be comfortable wearing western clothes in front of Champaklal. After a while, Champaklal himself solves this problem for them by deciding not to attend the party at all.

title: Ep. 195 - Daya Astonishes Everyone - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: All of Gokuldham has arrived for the birthday bash with full spirit and excitement. Babita has a superb entry being the birthday girl and is looking stunning. Daya steals the limelight and astonishes everybody with her unseen attire and look.

title: Ep. 196 - One Night, Two Different Plans - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: The Women of Gokuldham has decided to keep a Jagran for the well-being of their husbands and asks them to stay awake at night. The men hesitate at first, but eventually, they all agree because they decide to have their plan of having a party.

title: Ep. 197 - Realization - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: All the women are decked up for the Jagran and are ready to leave for the clubhouse whereas the men are waiting for their chance to begin the party at Taarak's place. All of them finally reach Taarak's place.

title: Ep. 198 - Battle Of Antakshari - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: As Taarak made all of the other men of Gokuldham realize that what they were doing was wrong, after realizing everybody goes to the Jagran to accompany their wives and also decides to play antakshari the whole night.

title: Ep. 199 - Meeting At Sodhi's - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Daya loses in the Antakshari deliberately so that everybody can sleep and makes Jethalal order food for everyone as everybody seemed hungry. This gesture of her's makes Champaklal and Jethalal proud. Later, all the residents gather at Sodi's house.

title: Ep. 200 - Gokuldham's  Anniversary Celebration Begins - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Taarak invites his friend as the chief guest for the Gokuldham society anniversary function. They conducted dance performance by the Gokuldam residents. The couples gave their debut in the rain dance performance.
